It includes your topic sentence and all the support sentences you wrote based on your idea web.<br /><br />&nbsp;</p><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"ju-powertip\" style=\"width: 100%;\"><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\">Remember!</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>When you write, you should always plan to go back over what you have written to revise and edit.</td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p>","rightText":"<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"ju-tableplain ju-tight\" style=\"width: 100%;\"><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>Body paragraph 1:</strong></p><p>The term &ldquo;positive attitude&rdquo; may sound vague and general, but it is quite easy to explain.&nbsp; Companies want employees who arrive at the office in a good mood, who leave their problems at home, and who have an upbeat approach to their jobs.&nbsp; A positive attitude involves taking on work with a smile without complaining.&nbsp; A good attitude also means having a &ldquo;can-do&rdquo; approach to the job; that means actively looking for solutions to problems rather than asking others to solve the problems for them.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p>"},{"settings":{"showAudio":1,"showNext":1,"showHeader":1,"hideRightPanel":0,"delayStep":0,"delayRight":0,"showRuler":0,"showRFB":1},"leftText":"<p>Review your thesis statement and your writing web to plan the second body paragraph of your contest essay.<br />&nbsp;</p>","rightText":"<p><img alt=\"The part of the writing web for your second body paragraph. There is nothing an interviewer loves more than talking to a candidate who is excited about the job, the company, and the opportunity.&nbsp; An enthusiastic candidate is not simply excited about the job; he or she expresses a strong desire to do well in the job and to make a strong contribution to the company&#39;s profits and growth.&nbsp; The best candidates research the company and its products before interviewing, and they talk openly about their excitement.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p>"},{"settings":{"showAudio":1,"showNext":1,"showHeader":1,"hideRightPanel":0,"delayStep":0,"delayRight":0,"showRuler":0,"showRFB":1},"leftText":"<p>Review your thesis statement and your writing web to plan the third body paragraph of your contest essay.<br />&nbsp;</p>","rightText":"<p><img alt=\"The part of the writing web for your third body paragraph.
